    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":2481,"title":"Bentonville School Board approves staff bonus","topic":"Education","slug":"bentonville-school-board-approves-staff-bonus","coverImage":null,"photoCredit":"Bentonville School District","date":"2020-11-27","content":"<p>The School Board met Tuesday and <a title=\"https://www.5newsonline.com/article/news/local/bentonville-school-staff-to-receive-bonuses/527-2d70950c-c830-4182-9424-045ec04b736d\" href=\"https://www.5newsonline.com/article/news/local/bentonville-school-staff-to-receive-bonuses/527-2d70950c-c830-4182-9424-045ec04b736d\">unanimously approved</a> a one-time payment to employees of the Bentonville School District.</p><ul><li><div>The bonus is to be 1.2% of each employee&#39;s contract amount, with a cap of $1,000. &quot;The bonuses will be paid Dec. 17. The average bonus will be about $670 and will cost the district $1.6 million, according to Deputy Superintendent Janet Schwanhausser. The district has about 2,300 employees.</div><div>&quot; - <a title=\"https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2020/nov/24/bentonville-school-board-approves-bonus-for-staff/\" href=\"https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2020/nov/24/bentonville-school-board-approves-bonus-for-staff/\">NWA Democrat Gazette</a></div><div><a title=\"https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2020/nov/24/bentonville-school-board-approves-bonus-for-staff/\" href=\"https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2020/nov/24/bentonville-school-board-approves-bonus-for-staff/\"></a></div></li></ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"bentonville-school-board-approves-staff-bonus"}},
